WEBVTT

00:02:20.027 --> 00:02:24.824
<i>The blue skies above are hopelessly clear</i>

00:02:24.824 --> 00:02:29.997
<i>At my wit's end, I feel a growing frustration</i>

00:02:30.413 --> 00:02:35.085
<i>As if to laugh at us hopeless cowards</i>

00:02:35.085 --> 00:02:38.588
<i>Countless eyes stare at us</i>

00:02:39.046 --> 00:02:45.012
<i>This soul of mine breaks again and again</i>

00:02:45.304 --> 00:02:48.223
<i>All I can do is hold it tight</i>

00:02:49.432 --> 00:02:54.479
<i>Until the day it turns to ash</i>

00:02:54.729 --> 00:02:57.316
<i>I've absorbed all of this sorrow</i>

00:02:57.441 --> 00:03:01.944
<i>It has shaped me, painted me</i>

00:03:02.069 --> 00:03:04.781
<i>But that's how we got here, right?</i>

00:03:04.907 --> 00:03:09.745
<i>One step at a time, just like breathing</i>

00:03:09.870 --> 00:03:12.288
<i>These countless scars on my palm</i>

00:03:12.413 --> 00:03:14.290
<i>That no longer fade</i>

00:03:14.415 --> 00:03:18.044
<i>Are my badge, my story</i>

00:03:18.336 --> 00:03:22.007
<i>I faced the fear and shred it to pieces</i>

00:03:22.132 --> 00:03:25.092
<i>And let it walk beside me once more</i>

00:03:25.092 --> 00:03:30.056
BLEACH: THOUSAND-YEAR BLOOD WAR

00:03:49.742 --> 00:03:51.161
Hey, Shunsui!

00:03:51.161 --> 00:03:54.372
How dare you enter my room
without my permission again!

00:03:54.372 --> 00:03:56.375
I know, I'm sorry, my bad!

00:03:56.375 --> 00:03:58.961
What kind of apology is that?!

00:03:59.252 --> 00:04:00.586
Unforgivable!

00:04:00.586 --> 00:04:02.088
I mean it!

00:04:02.088 --> 00:04:04.423
I'm sorry I snuck in,
but I was surprised

00:04:04.423 --> 00:04:06.759
you had a painting hanging,
Old Man Yama, so...

00:04:08.262 --> 00:04:09.805
Damn old geezer...

00:04:09.805 --> 00:04:14.810
That's a monster that appeared in
the Soul Society a long time ago.

00:04:15.978 --> 00:04:19.146
It showed up when the Soul Society
was facing a crisis...

00:04:19.814 --> 00:04:22.108
only to make things much worse.

00:04:24.653 --> 00:04:26.612
It will never show up again.

00:04:27.322 --> 00:04:30.367
But if it ever does...

00:04:31.201 --> 00:04:32.744
<i>Then...</i>

00:04:52.889 --> 00:04:56.851
<i>...I'll probably never
be back here again.</i>

00:05:01.982 --> 00:05:03.817
Old Man Yama!!

00:05:26.589 --> 00:05:28.841
You may have been
the head of the Soul Reapers...

00:05:29.718 --> 00:05:34.805
but your demise was pitiful,
Shigekuni Yamamoto.

00:05:37.725 --> 00:05:39.810
Let's go, Haschwalth.

00:05:39.810 --> 00:05:40.853
Yes, sir.

00:05:50.863 --> 00:05:53.867
Trying to show that you won't
let me get away even in death?

00:05:55.076 --> 00:05:56.411
Pathetic.

00:05:57.245 --> 00:06:00.415
Shigekuni Yamamoto,
you half-hearted fool.

00:06:00.915 --> 00:06:04.752
You will never know
why I removed you

00:06:04.752 --> 00:06:07.963
from being counted as
one of the five Special Threats.

00:06:09.423 --> 00:06:12.968
Why didn't you restore
your left arm?

00:06:14.512 --> 00:06:19.600
You could've done so if you'd
ordered that human girl to.

00:06:20.685 --> 00:06:21.685
I know why.

00:06:22.062 --> 00:06:25.148
You didn't want to exploit humans.

00:06:25.940 --> 00:06:27.401
I know all about it.

00:06:27.817 --> 00:06:30.737
Even during your battle with Aizen,

00:06:30.903 --> 00:06:33.656
you were apprehensive about
getting Ichigo Kurosaki involved

00:06:33.656 --> 00:06:35.826
because he was a human.

00:06:36.326 --> 00:06:40.747
And even now, you stood before me
trying to carry the burden of

00:06:40.747 --> 00:06:44.834
the Soul Society and the World
of the Living on your shoulders...

00:06:45.334 --> 00:06:47.086
and you lost.

00:06:48.588 --> 00:06:51.925
You've grown weak,
Shigekuni Yamamoto.

00:06:52.634 --> 00:06:54.468
You used to be different.

00:06:55.595 --> 00:06:58.639
The original Thirteen Court Guard
Squads that you founded

00:06:58.639 --> 00:07:00.934
were Court Guards in name only.

00:07:00.934 --> 00:07:04.062
They were a group of
savage killers.

00:07:04.271 --> 00:07:07.690
But because of that,
they were a fearsome bunch.

00:07:07.983 --> 00:07:10.026
And as their leader,
Shigekuni Yamamoto,

00:07:10.026 --> 00:07:12.571
you were truly a beast
with the sword...

00:07:12.821 --> 00:07:15.740
You used everything and anything
to slay an enemy.

00:07:15.740 --> 00:07:18.367
The lives of the people,
including your own subordinates,

00:07:18.367 --> 00:07:21.370
weighed only as much as ash to you.

00:07:22.079 --> 00:07:27.168
But that all changed after
you exterminated us Quincies.

00:07:28.170 --> 00:07:29.879
Upon gaining a peaceful world,

00:07:29.879 --> 00:07:33.716
you people had more things
to protect and to love.

00:07:33.716 --> 00:07:36.136
You've deteriorated into
a bunch of weaklings

00:07:36.136 --> 00:07:37.303
who would hesitate to take action

00:07:37.303 --> 00:07:39.889
to satisfy your pathetic
sense of justice and pride.

00:07:40.973 --> 00:07:45.562
You died without realizing this,
so I'm going to tell you.

00:07:47.230 --> 00:07:50.399
The Soul Society
is about to perish.

00:07:51.026 --> 00:07:57.656
But the Thirteen Court Guard Squads
died with us a thousand years ago!

00:08:13.839 --> 00:08:14.925
Time to finish this.

00:08:15.800 --> 00:08:18.802
Inform every member
of the Stern Ritter.

00:08:20.679 --> 00:08:25.601
Tell them to thoroughly...
crush the Soul Society!

00:08:36.863 --> 00:08:38.240
- Wha—?!
- What's that?!

00:08:45.371 --> 00:08:47.874
Advance, Soldat!

00:08:49.793 --> 00:08:51.211
Rebel army foot soldiers!

00:08:51.836 --> 00:08:53.837
Stand your ground!
We can take them—

00:09:20.948 --> 00:09:22.576
Th-They're too strong...

00:09:22.741 --> 00:09:24.827
M-Must get help...!

00:09:41.595 --> 00:09:42.928
It's over.

00:09:55.024 --> 00:09:56.150
Don't disappear!

00:09:57.902 --> 00:09:58.695
Don't disappear!

00:10:01.697 --> 00:10:02.907
Don't disappear!

00:10:06.035 --> 00:10:08.705
Don't disappear!

00:10:11.582 --> 00:10:13.460
Finally...

00:10:13.793 --> 00:10:20.174
Sorry, I wanted to open it sooner
from this side, but...

00:10:20.799 --> 00:10:24.763
things never seem...
to go the way we want...

00:10:25.596 --> 00:10:27.932
Huh?
Who the hell are you?

00:10:28.642 --> 00:10:31.061
I'm Stern Ritter, Shaz Domino!

00:10:31.352 --> 00:10:32.812
The power I was given is—

00:10:40.945 --> 00:10:42.404
Hey, hang in there!

00:10:59.172 --> 00:11:00.673
The Spiritual Pressure
disappeared?!

00:11:00.673 --> 00:11:02.049
What was that just now?!

00:11:15.688 --> 00:11:18.817
Rukia and Renji...

00:11:19.900 --> 00:11:21.860
were they still alive?

00:11:22.861 --> 00:11:23.779
Yeah.

00:11:23.779 --> 00:11:24.864
Don't worry.

00:11:25.532 --> 00:11:26.533
They're alive.

00:11:28.368 --> 00:11:29.744
I see...

00:11:30.703 --> 00:11:32.038
Thank goodness...

00:11:34.832 --> 00:11:39.796
I don't have... much time left.

00:11:42.215 --> 00:11:45.759
Though I am a captain of
the Thirteen Court Guard Squads,

00:11:46.052 --> 00:11:48.096
I was unable to defeat

00:11:48.638 --> 00:11:51.765
the despicable people
who trampled on the Seireitei.

00:11:52.808 --> 00:11:56.019
I led many squad members
to their deaths...

00:11:56.770 --> 00:11:58.105
I brought sorrow

00:11:58.105 --> 00:12:00.649
to their subordinates
and to their families...

00:12:01.400 --> 00:12:06.322
Only to lose and die in disgrace.

00:12:07.197 --> 00:12:09.158
I am deeply ashamed of this.

00:12:12.745 --> 00:12:15.831
You, on the other hand,
are a human.

00:12:16.291 --> 00:12:20.669
Not only should you not be
involved in this fight...

00:12:20.961 --> 00:12:24.631
you should not even be here
in the first place.

00:12:25.759 --> 00:12:27.719
So forgive me

00:12:27.719 --> 00:12:34.808
for the terrible audacity
of asking you this final favor...

00:12:38.104 --> 00:12:39.105
Please...

00:12:40.315 --> 00:12:43.234
protect the Soul Society...

00:12:43.777 --> 00:12:45.778
Ichigo Kurosaki...!

00:13:09.052 --> 00:13:10.260
This Spiritual Pressure...

00:13:10.803 --> 00:13:13.222
Yes, it must be Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:13:14.264 --> 00:13:15.808
Shall I purge him?

00:13:16.850 --> 00:13:18.311
No. Let's go.

00:13:30.490 --> 00:13:32.033
You...!

00:13:56.224 --> 00:13:58.684
<i>I didn't get a response.</i>

00:14:00.019 --> 00:14:01.437
<i>That's fine.</i>

00:14:02.020 --> 00:14:04.774
<i>That's the kind of man he is.</i>

00:14:05.817 --> 00:14:08.778
<i>I know his answer
even if he didn't respond.</i>

00:14:13.490 --> 00:14:18.580
I'm counting on you,
Ichigo Kurosaki...

00:14:36.556 --> 00:14:37.890
Your Majesty, I'll handle this...

00:14:39.767 --> 00:14:41.144
Ichigo Kurosaki...

00:14:41.727 --> 00:14:43.687
I don't know how you did it,

00:14:44.062 --> 00:14:46.399
but I'm impressed
you broke out of Quilge's "Jail."

00:14:46.941 --> 00:14:51.738
But do you really intend to
fight me in that ragged state?

00:14:52.654 --> 00:14:54.698
Are you the enemy leader?

00:14:55.783 --> 00:14:57.451
The "enemy," huh?

00:14:58.494 --> 00:14:59.620
I am.

00:14:59.828 --> 00:15:01.748
But you could also say
that I'm not.

00:15:02.916 --> 00:15:04.625
Cut the crap!

00:15:05.043 --> 00:15:09.129
I'm asking if you're the one
who wrecked the Soul Society!

00:15:09.589 --> 00:15:11.591
I did indeed.

00:15:14.844 --> 00:15:15.845
Your Majesty...

00:15:15.970 --> 00:15:18.722
As you can see, Haschwalth...

00:15:19.014 --> 00:15:21.100
he leaves me with no choice.

00:15:21.643 --> 00:15:23.144
I will crush him here.

00:16:06.645 --> 00:16:07.647
Getsuga...

00:16:08.563 --> 00:16:11.274
...tensho!

00:16:38.260 --> 00:16:40.221
He should still be alive.

00:16:41.054 --> 00:16:42.432
Carry him to the castle.

00:16:42.557 --> 00:16:45.559
We'll revive him
and put him under my command.

00:16:46.769 --> 00:16:47.854
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:16:57.029 --> 00:16:58.030
<i>Impossible...!</i>

00:16:58.698 --> 00:16:59.699
<i>Is that...</i>

00:17:00.700 --> 00:17:02.242
<i>Blut Vene?!</i>

00:17:05.872 --> 00:17:06.873
Your Majesty!

00:17:14.337 --> 00:17:15.923
Should have known better...

00:17:17.299 --> 00:17:18.634
What's that?

00:17:18.634 --> 00:17:22.221
You think you won just because
you withstood a few of my attacks?

00:17:22.596 --> 00:17:24.097
That's not what I meant.

00:17:33.607 --> 00:17:34.608
I was right...

00:17:35.151 --> 00:17:37.111
I wasn't imagining it.

00:17:37.862 --> 00:17:39.238
What are you talking about?

00:17:39.780 --> 00:17:45.327
It seems that using Quilge Opie
to keep you at bay was a mistake...

00:17:45.661 --> 00:17:50.708
I should have used an Arrancar
instead of a trueborn Quincy...

00:17:51.084 --> 00:17:55.712
Because of that, the memories
within your Spiritual Pressure

00:17:55.712 --> 00:17:58.382
have awakened too soon.

00:17:59.092 --> 00:18:02.636
You kept releasing
your Spiritual Pressure to the limit

00:18:02.636 --> 00:18:05.013
while in contact with
Quilge's "Jail"

00:18:05.013 --> 00:18:06.598
in order to destroy it.

00:18:07.349 --> 00:18:10.978
The bits of Spiritual Pressure left
behind from this explosive release

00:18:11.186 --> 00:18:13.689
mixed with some of
Quilge's Spiritual Pressure

00:18:13.689 --> 00:18:15.607
as it returned to your body.

00:18:16.776 --> 00:18:19.569
His Quincy Spiritual Pressure

00:18:19.569 --> 00:18:23.950
slowly seeped into
the depths of your soul,

00:18:23.950 --> 00:18:27.411
drawing out memories
within your Spiritual Pressure

00:18:27.411 --> 00:18:29.038
from its core...

00:18:30.413 --> 00:18:34.126
Quilge's "Jail" is meant to
restrain enemies...

00:18:34.876 --> 00:18:38.297
It is unable to contain Quincies!

00:18:39.673 --> 00:18:41.800
What... are you talking about?

00:18:42.676 --> 00:18:44.470
Memories within
my Spiritual Pressure?

00:18:44.886 --> 00:18:46.763
What's this about Quincies?

00:18:47.431 --> 00:18:48.598
I see...

00:18:49.142 --> 00:18:52.269
You don't know anything
about yourself, do you?

00:18:53.563 --> 00:18:54.646
Not even about...

00:18:55.565 --> 00:18:56.898
your own mother.

00:19:00.236 --> 00:19:04.990
My plan was to take you back
and slowly re-educate you...

00:19:04.990 --> 00:19:06.075
What are you—?

00:19:06.784 --> 00:19:10.538
...but I no longer have the luxury
of doing that.

00:19:10.538 --> 00:19:11.622
What are you—?

00:19:12.498 --> 00:19:14.333
I've decided to force you
into submission

00:19:14.333 --> 00:19:15.917
and drag you with me!

00:19:17.295 --> 00:19:20.173
I said, what the hell
are you talking about?!

00:19:20.423 --> 00:19:22.967
I'll tell you at the Wandenreich.

00:19:28.681 --> 00:19:30.724
Qualkreis!

00:19:31.767 --> 00:19:32.518
Now then...

00:19:32.518 --> 00:19:35.645
Show me what you've got,
Ichigo Kurosaki!

00:19:42.236 --> 00:19:45.990
Getsugatensho!

00:20:14.809 --> 00:20:16.770
I will pierce you this time!

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:19.731
Don't assume you can evade it
with your Blut Vene!

00:20:20.232 --> 00:20:21.692
My—

00:20:26.821 --> 00:20:27.823
This is...

00:20:30.701 --> 00:20:32.411
It is time, Your Majesty.

00:20:32.953 --> 00:20:35.748
We've reached our limit for working
outside of the Schatten Bereich.

00:20:36.289 --> 00:20:37.916
Please return to the Wandenreich.

00:20:38.667 --> 00:20:39.460
Impossible.

00:20:39.460 --> 00:20:41.127
We should still have time to—

00:20:44.006 --> 00:20:47.300
Of course.
Sosuke Aizen...

00:20:47.969 --> 00:20:49.929
This is one of his tricks.

00:20:50.136 --> 00:20:52.222
During the few minutes
I was in contact with him,

00:20:52.222 --> 00:20:55.643
he slightly altered my senses...

00:20:56.602 --> 00:21:00.105
Haschwalth, you knew
but kept quiet, didn't you?

00:21:00.772 --> 00:21:02.775
I figured it would be pointless
to try to stop you.

00:21:04.734 --> 00:21:05.861
Well, it doesn't matter.

00:21:06.653 --> 00:21:07.654
Let's go.

00:21:16.913 --> 00:21:19.541
My time's up, so I'll be going now.

00:21:20.292 --> 00:21:22.877
I guess you can't hear me anymore...

00:21:30.720 --> 00:21:31.721
Stop!

00:21:32.430 --> 00:21:33.888
You think I'd let you go?

00:21:34.682 --> 00:21:37.768
After what you did
to the Soul Society...

00:21:38.519 --> 00:21:40.145
there's no way I'd let you escape!

00:21:42.981 --> 00:21:45.108
I said stop!

00:22:01.541 --> 00:22:04.295
Farewell, Ichigo Kurosaki.

00:22:04.961 --> 00:22:07.256
I'll come back for you again.

00:22:07.882 --> 00:22:10.384
Heal your wounds and wait...

00:22:12.635 --> 00:22:17.098
...my son... born in the dark...

00:22:28.109 --> 00:22:31.113
<i>Everything we had left behind</i>

00:22:31.279 --> 00:22:35.617
<i>Our breaths blending as mist</i>

00:22:35.742 --> 00:22:39.872
<i>without form or expression</i>

00:22:39.997 --> 00:22:44.167
<i>We lie buried as we glare
into the distance</i>

00:22:44.751 --> 00:22:47.128
<i>I can't hear anything</i>

00:22:47.253 --> 00:22:50.383
<i>I can't seem to cut anything</i>

00:22:50.508 --> 00:22:52.968
<i>It feels like I'm sinking</i>

00:22:53.094 --> 00:22:54.929
<i>Falling, falling</i>

00:22:54.929 --> 00:22:56.012
<i>Touching</i>

00:22:56.137 --> 00:22:59.517
<i>Eyes struck wide open</i>

00:22:59.517 --> 00:23:02.853
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:02.978 --> 00:23:09.151
<i>The furthest reaches are now visible to us</i>

00:23:09.527 --> 00:23:13.154
<i>It cannot be undone
and cannot be stopped</i>

00:23:13.279 --> 00:23:16.616
<i>This ensuing struggle</i>

00:23:16.616 --> 00:23:21.413
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:21.413 --> 00:23:23.540
<i>Along with our breaths</i>

00:23:23.749 --> 00:23:25.041
<i>Take everything</i>

00:23:25.041 --> 00:23:29.797
<i>Whisk it away beyond
the ends of the earth</i>

00:23:29.922 --> 00:23:31.840
<i>Along with our futures</i>

00:23:31.965 --> 00:23:33.717
<i>Along with our world</i>

00:23:34.801 --> 00:23:38.055
<i>Something no one has ever seen</i>

00:23:38.180 --> 00:23:44.644
<i>The furthest reaches are now
visible to us</i>

00:23:44.769 --> 00:23:48.441
<i>Don't you know God's demand?</i>

00:23:48.566 --> 00:23:51.943
<i>As we tear each other down</i>

00:24:00.869 --> 00:24:02.954
<i>"I look to the heavens
and chase that star."</i>

00:24:04.914 --> 00:24:08.751
<i>"Burned into my eyes,
the afterglow of its smoke."</i>

